ters) were made easy to reach","transliteration":"wadhullilat","root":"ذلل","lemmaId":null},{"id":"76:14:5","ayahNum":14,"wordNum":5,"word":"قُطُوفُهَا","meaning":"its fruits (referring to Paradise)","transliteration":"quṭūfuhā","root":"قطف","lemmaId":null},{"id":"76:14:6","ayahNum":14,"wordNum":6,"word":"تَذْلِيلًا","meaning":"making (something) completely accessible (object of وَذُلِّلَتْ)","transliteration":"tadhlīlan","root":"ذلل","lemmaId":null},{"id":"76:15:1","ayahNum":15,"wordNum":1,"word":"وَيُطَافُ","meaning":"and is being circled around (with servants circling around them with vessels)","transliteration":"wayuṭāfu","root":"طوف","lemmaId":2385},{"id":"76:15:2","ayahNum":15,"wordNum":2,"word":"عَلَيْهِم","meaning":"upon them (referring to the people being served in paradise)","transliteration":"ʿalayhim","root":"","lemmaId":2582},{"id":"76:15:3","ayahNum":15,"wordNum":3,"word":"بِـَٔانِيَةٍ","meaning":"with a vessel (used to serve drinks in this ayah)","transliteration":"biāniyatin","root":"أني","lemmaId":28},{"id":"76:15:4","ayahNum":15,"wordNum":4,"word":"مِّن","meaning":"from (connects to فِضَّةٍ)","transliteration":"min","root":"","lemmaId":3464},{"id":"76:15:5","ayahNum":15,"wordNum":5,"word":"فِضَّةٍ","meaning":"of silver (describing the vessels in آنِيَةٍ)","transliteration":"fiḍḍatin","root":"فضض","lemmaId":null},{"id":"76:15:6","ayahNum":15,"wordNum":6,"word":"وَأَكْوَابٍ","meaning":"and cups/goblets (being circulated with)","transliteration":"wa-akwābin","root":"كوب","lemmaId":null},{"id":"76:15:7","ayahNum":15,"wordNum":7,"word":"كَانَتْ","meaning":"it was (referring to the vessels of silver mentioned before)","transliteration":"kānat","root":"كون","lemmaId":null},{"id":"76:15:8","ayahNum":15,"wordNum":8,"word":"قَوَارِيرَا۠","meaning":"vessels/containers (made of crystal) - pause form","transliteration":"qawārīrā","root":"قرر","lemmaId":null},{"id":"76:16:1","ayahNum":16,"wordNum":1,"word":"قَوَارِيرَا۟","meaning":"glass vessels (acted on)","tra